破产，其后忽觉有负玲的爱，而和玲结婚有准备重振旗鼓，向冠鹤挑战，而冷落爱玲，终于有大获全胜，随即要与玲完婚，但内心对浅无法忘情。友有集结各富豪资金，准备于大陆兴建马场，但因政府抨击赛马赌博化，而导致有和凤双双身亡.";s:13:"vod_play_from";s:9:"zuidam3u8";s:15:"vod_play_server";s:2:"no";s:13:"vod_play_note";s:0:"";s:12:"vod_play_url";s:3039:"第01集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6351_4ae9f615/index.m3u8#第02集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6350_285e5a4d/index.m3u8#第03集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6349_56f2bbb8/index.m3u8#第04集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6348_da261792/index.m3u8#第05集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6347_3e350972/index.m3u8#第06集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6346_d7d60577/index.m3u8#第07集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6345_916fde49/index.m3u8#第08集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6344_59532d40/index.m3u8#第09集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6343_8c09b7e0/index.m3u8#第10集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6342_62890267/index.m3u8#第11集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6341_995cde30/index.m3u8#第12集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6340_2203459f/index.m3u8#第13集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6339_b40ba534/index.m3u8#第14集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6338_0135c684/index.m3u8#第15集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6337_fe4ab5d4/index.m3u8#第16集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6336_553a19ec/index.m3u8#第17集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6335_a271a9c0/index.m3u8#第18集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6334_ff6306d8/index.m3u8#第19集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6333_ba170076/index.m3u8#第20集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6332_7a8b3859/index.m3u8#第21集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6331_bcdf3b0c/index.m3u8#第22集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6330_ab05dc39/index.m3u8#第23集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6329_48c1fcd3/index.m3u8#第24集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/20190809/6328_a7b92e95/index.m3u8#第25集$http://yanzishan.shuhu-zuida.com/